  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK773">
<l>pērāṇmai yeṉpa taṟukaṇoṉ ṟuṟṟakkā</l>
<l>lūrāṇmai maṟṟata ṉeḵku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned say that fierceness (incontest with a foe) is indeed great valour but to become a benefactor in case of accident (to a foe) is the extreme (limit) of that valour.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
